episodes.title: Unredacted Epstein files trigger Republican outrage
episodes.description:
Access to the unredacted Epstein files is sparking outrage on Capitol Hill, as members of Congress demand accountability for those involved in trafficking and abusing women and girls.

In this episode of Behind the Curtain, Axios co-founder Jim VandeHei breaks down why the Epstein saga is far from over, and which powerful figures could still face consequences.
